            span.breadcrumb-separator /
            span.breadcrumb-item.breadcrumb-current Article Title Placeholder

      // Main Content Body
      section.article-content-section.section
        .container
          .article-content-layout
            .article-content-main
              // Featured Image
              .article-featured-image-placeholder FEATURED IMAGE

              // Article Header
              .article-header-main
                .article-category Case Study
                h1.article-title Article Title Placeholder - This Can Span Multiple Lines If Needed
                .article-meta
                  span.article-meta-item Jan 15, 2025
                  span.article-meta-separator ·
                  span.article-meta-item 5 min read
                  span.article-meta-separator ·
                  span.article-meta-item Author Name Placeholder
                .article-intro
                  p This is a placeholder introduction paragraph that provides context for the article. It should be approximately two to three lines long and give readers a clear understanding of what the article will cover. This summary helps set expectations before diving into the detailed content.

              // Article Content Sections
              // Section: Background
              h2.article-content-heading Background
              p.article-content-paragraph This is a placeholder paragraph for the background section. It provides context and sets the stage for understanding the challenges and solutions discussed in this article. The content should be informative and help readers understand the situation before diving into specific details.
              p.article-content-paragraph This is a second paragraph in the background section. It continues to build context and may include additional details about the circumstances, requirements, or initial conditions that led to the need for the logistics solution described in this case study or article.
              p.article-content-paragraph A third paragraph may provide further context or historical information that helps readers fully understand the background and context of the situation being discussed.

              // Section: Challenges
              h2.article-content-heading Challenges
              ul.article-content-list
                li Challenge placeholder 1: Description of the first major challenge encountered in this scenario.
                li Challenge placeholder 2: Description of the second major challenge that needed to be addressed.
                li Challenge placeholder 3: Description of additional challenges or constraints that impacted the logistics process.

              // Section: TailorMed Solution
              h2.article-content-heading TailorMed Solution
              p.article-content-paragraph This paragraph describes the solution approach taken by TailorMed to address the challenges mentioned above. It explains the methodology, processes, and specific steps implemented to ensure successful delivery and compliance.
              p.article-content-paragraph A second paragraph may detail specific technologies, packaging systems, or operational procedures that were utilized as part of the solution. This helps readers understand the practical implementation of the approach.
              ul.article-content-list
                li Solution component 1: Description of a key element of the solution.
                li Solution component 2: Description of another important aspect of the solution.
                li Solution component 3: Additional solution elements that contributed to success.

            // Sidebar - Key Details & Download (right side)
            .article-sidebar
              .sidebar-widget
                h3.sidebar-widget-title Key Details
                .key-details-list
                  .key-detail-item
                    .key-detail-label Industry
                    .key-detail-value Biotech
                  .key-detail-item
                    .key-detail-label Shipment type
                    .key-detail-value Research samples
                  .key-detail-item
                    .key-detail-label Temperature range
                    .key-detail-value -80°C
                  .key-detail-item
                    .key-detail-label Origin / Destination
                    .key-detail-value Taipei to Boston
              .sidebar-widget
                h3.sidebar-widget-title Download / Related Document
                a.btn.btn-secondary(href="#") Download PDF

      // Article Footer Actions
      section.article-footer-section.section
        .container
          .article-footer-divider
          .article-back-link
            a.article-back-link-text(href="case-studies.html") ← Back to Resources
          .article-footer-cta
            h3.article-footer-cta-title Have a similar logistics challenge?
            p.article-footer-cta-subtitle Contact our team to discuss a tailored solution.
            a.btn.btn-primary(href="../../contact/") Contact Us

